SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4968
A bill to amend 2018 PA 175, entitled
"Insurance provider assessment act,"
by amending sections 7, 11, and 17 (MCL 550.1757, 550.1761, and
550.1767).
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
