20 determined each year by the department of health and human services
21 for the dollar amount necessary per member month to achieve a total
22 revenue not to exceed the total revenue due for the tax year of
23 April 1, 2024 through March 31, 2025. The per member month tax rate
24 must be the same for all tiers described in subsection (1).
